# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Baraza Protocol — Local Development Template
# Copy to .env.local and fill in your values.
# Do NOT commit .env.local — it contains real secrets.
#
# These defaults point to testnet/sandbox services so you can
# run `npm run dev` without spending real money.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


